---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Joe Cardoso" description="About Joe Cardoso - Software Engineer specializing in observability and full-stack development">
  
  <section class="about-content">
    <h2>$ whoami</h2>
    <p>
      Hello there! I'm Joe, a full-stack software engineer based in Toronto, Canada.
    </p>

    <h2>$ cat journey.txt</h2>
    <p>
    My journey began at Texas A&M pursuing a Master's degree in Mechanical Engineering. Using <a href="https://www.mathworks.com/products/matlab.html">MatLab</a> often made me realize how much I enjoyed the process of writing software. After graduating and experiencing the world a bit, I realized I would be much happier working on something I'm deeply passionate about, instead of keeping within the guardrails of formal education.
    </p>

    <p>
    But for this career choice to make sense I needed to be sure I'd be working on true engineering problems, not just assembly-line development. That's when my partnership with <a href="https://launchschool.com">Launch School</a> came about. Our interests aligned wonderfully. Their <a href="https://public.launchschool.com/mastery">mastery-based approach</a> fosters a community where the spirit of excellence is contagious, with engineers who've landed at top companies not by cutting corners, but by building unshakeable foundations.
    </p>

    <p>
    Through that community, I was lucky enough to partner up with some brilliant folks and together we built <a href="https://vispyr.com">Vispyr</a>, an open-source observability tool combining continuous profiling with telemetry. We built automated AWS deployment pipelines, created custom Grafana dashboards, integrated Tempo, Pyroscope, and Prometheus into a single CLI-driven deployment that gives you code-level visibility into production performance.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="contact">
    <h2>$ echo $CONTACT</h2>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/JoeCardoso13" target="_blank">github</a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/joe-cardoso-eng" target="_blank">linkedin</a>
      <a href="mailto:jow13_122@yahoo.com">email</a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EfSqsX6bY4eiO0OrUqJWbG1G9tIrha7h/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank">resume</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content p {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
